Sure, here are some examples:

1. *Amin*, molim te pročitaj ovaj tekst. (Amen, please read this text.)
2. Ovo je *amin* voda za piće. (This is pure drinking *amen* water.)
3. Ne treba da lažeš, *amin*! (Don't lie, *amen*!)
4. Svi su rekli *amin* nakon molitve. (Everyone said *amen* after the prayer.)
5. Želim da ti kažem nešto, *amin*. (I want to tell you something, *amen*.)
6. Da li si čuo da je novi pastor došao u crkvu *amin*? (Have you heard that a new pastor came to the church, *amen*?)
7. Završili smo projekat *amin*! (We finished the project, *amen*!)
8. Molim vas, recite *amin* nakon što izgovorim rečenicu. (Please say *amen* after I say the sentence.)

I hope these examples help!